        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            Google & GitHub OAuth
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            Email confirmation
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            Secure password reset
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3: Team Management -->
      <div class="glass-card-light rounded-2xl p-8" data-scroll-animator-target="item" data-animation="fade-up" data-delay="300">
        <div class="feature-icon w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Team Management</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Invite team members via email with role-based permissions. Complete invitation workflow with expiration.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            Email invitations
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
